  "remarks": "MFI Soft LLC is a Russian IT company that develops and manufactures hardware and software for Russia’s System for Operational-search Measures (SORM) capabilities. SORM enables Russia’s domestic and foreign intelligence collection, monitoring and suppression of dissent, and has been installed on infrastructure in occupied parts of Ukraine to further aid Russia’s attempts to integrate Ukraine’s territory into Russia. Therefore, MFI Soft LLC is materially supporting and benefitting from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}